%^CYAN%^BOLD%^ASSASSIN%^RESET%^

While others prefer to stand boldly in the face of danger, your preferred weapon is stealth and silence. When you attack, your enemy is bound to fall.

%^BOLD%^Trance:%^RESET%^
Skill Bonus : Stealth
Trance Bonus : Attack Damage Bonus

%^BOLD%^Maneuver:%^RESET%^
Spend psionic focus to perform a mental damage attack

